PG| ***** 2 ***** |


cp|8|AT|

^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|I have a slight preference for natural (actually I use transfer overcalls which I will explain in a minute) but DONT works pretty well too. There is no perfect way to compete against a weak NT, which is one reason I play it. |
PG| ***** 3 ***** |


AT|

In "Transfer Overcalls", an overcall over 1NT is a transfer (e.g 1N-2D is a heart transfer.). The reason that works slightly better is because a) the 2@D bidder can continue bidding when appropriate since partner can't pass and b) the responder to the 2@D bidder can make other bids besides just accepting the transfer when they have a good hand. So I think it is a little more flexible than just natural overcalls. However, for this session we will use natural. So let us get started.|
