Based on the auction, West has 6 spades, Anna has 5 spades between the 2 hands, so East has 2 spades - 7-5=2. Moreover, the @SJ lead means that West has the @SA. So if Anna ducks the first spade, she can guarantee that if East ever gets in, he will be out of spades.|
